Netsoc server setup scripts

ldap-server2 and ldap-client2 refer to the new setup with the new schema. The old ones should not be needed but are left there for record until all old servers/setups have been decomissioned

These are scripts to setup services/daemons/whatever 

List of services 

Finished:
*ssh server 
*ldap client (libpam-ldapd)
*ldap server
*web-wordpress

Workong on:
*web-forum

Planned:
*web-wiki

*dns server
*client program groups



This may be  half replaced by deb packages in our own repo later
